00:44:28,710 --> 00:44:29,690
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}闭嘴

678
00:44:30,880 --> 00:44:32,290
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}多谢了

