00:44:32,380 --> 00:44:33,860
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}听着

680
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:38,260
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}如果你见到卢克的话

