00:45:09,820 --> 00:45:11,360
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}再次感谢

690
00:45:13,220 --> 00:45:14,760
{\fnSTXihei\fs20\1c&HC0C0C0&}他不会成功的

